snippet.title: Blood Bowl 3 | Season 3: Shambling Undead Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome in Season 3, Coaches! We're diving deep into the dark and eerie world of the Shambling Undead team in Blood Bowl 3. Unleash the undead mayhem as we introduce you to this spine-chilling team, combining the cunning strategy of Necromancy with the raw power of the afterlife!


Steam: https://nacon.me/BB3Steam
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BloodBowl_Game
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bloodbowlgame
